==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unable
<hw>Un*a"ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not able; not having sufficient strength, means, knowledge, skill, or the like; impotent; weak; helpless; incapable; -- now usually followed by an infinitive or an adverbial phrase; <as>as, <ex>unable</ex> for work; <ex>unable</ex> to bear fatigue</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Sapless age and weak <qex>unable</qex> limbs.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unabled</ent>⟦br⟧
